data.description: Lovely 3 Bedroom Home in Fountain! New interior paint throughout! Property backs to open space, feels like country living with all the city amenities! Located in Countryside neighborhood on cul-de-sac, covered front porch enters to living room with soaring ceilings and plenty of natural lighting! Open main level floor plan, dining area walks out to concrete patio and nearly quarter acre lot with fenced backyard and storage shed! Nothing but country and field behind home provides privacy hard to come by in the city! Kitchen features gorgeous complimenatry cabinetry, pantry off dining room and stainless steel appliances! East laundry access with washer/dryer included, half bath and 2 attached garage! Master suite on upper level features walk in closet and attached jack and jill bath! Two additional bedrooms on upper level. Unfinished basement with rough in equals untapped equity potential! Additional property amenities include central A/C installed 2020 and a brand new roof! Located close to Fort Carson, schools, parks and more!
